This paper deals with logical reasoning and entailment, which are core topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and mathematical logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the comparison and equivalence of different preferential entailment models, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper touches upon the simplification of models, which is relevant to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
